-- MOVES-Tom Marano joins TowerBrook Capital's management advisory board
-- 
-- Wed Sep 24, 2014 11:33AM EDT
-- None



Sept 24 (Reuters) - Investment firm TowerBrook Capital Partners LP appointed Tom Marano to its management advisory board.

Marano joins TowerBrook from ResCap, a subsidiary of Ally Financial Inc <ALLY.N>, where he was most recently the chief executive. He will help TowerBrook, which has offices in New York and London, develop investment opportunities in the financial services sector with a focus on the residential mortgage industry.